text: Inni (Rabbiin) Isa samiifi dachii guyyoota jaha keessatti uumeedhaArshiin Isaas bishaan gubbaa tureEenyuu keessantu dalagaan isaa irra gaarii ta’uu isin qormaatuuf (isaan uume)Yoo ati “Dhugumatti isin du’a booda kaafamoodha” jetteen, isaan kafaran “kun sihrii ifa ta’e malee waan biraatii miti” jedhu
